longBusinessSummary: Elah Holdings, Inc. does not have significant operations. It intends to acquire businesses in the commercial and industrial markets. The company was formerly known as Real Industry, Inc. and changed its name to Elah Holdings, Inc. in May 2018. Elah Holdings, Inc. was incorporated in 1972 and is based in Dallas, Texas.
